智利揮別獨裁政體後，今年也向已執政20年的中間偏左政黨[民主政黨聯盟](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concert_of_Parties_for_Democracy
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concert_of_Parties_for_Democracy")告別，自從獨裁者皮諾契（Augusto
Pinochet）政權於1990垮台後，該黨便執政至今，如今終於由右翼候選人皮涅拉（[Sebatián Piñera
Echeñique](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebastian_Pi%C3%B1era
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebastian_Piñera")）宣告當選總統。

